{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9f970d274c","title":"毛泽东对邓小平关于高岗、饶漱石反党联盟的报告稿的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5df7053aab","index":0,"year":1955,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"9f970d274c"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"88d89d3bed","name":"饶漱石","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6257402f57","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对邓小平关于高岗、饶漱石反党联盟的报告稿的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"ceec04af5d","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"88083980f1","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、陈、彭真、小平阅后，交恩来同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"237b094208","type":"paragraph","text":"高、饶联盟文件已看了一遍，全文可用，作了一些修改，主要是从第九页起括掉了两段，因为我觉得这个问题不宜这样地在这里辩论，括掉后似乎要好一些，请你们斟酌。刘、陈、彭、邓各同志的修改意见，请于日内即交恩来，以便明日或后日谈一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"3d911273e6","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"51104c5893","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"},{"id":"ff4e66a05a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内曾经出现过陈独秀、张国焘等著名的大叛徒，他们都是阶级敌人在我们党内的代理人，我们曾经进行严肃的斗争驱逐了这些叛徒。有些同志觉得高饶反党联盟是难以理解的现象，这是不了解党的历史、阶级斗争的历史和现状的原<缘>故。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c"}],"page":{"id":"33a49af87e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9f970d274c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}